        <name>XDfeCcf_multiAddCC_1xNR100_3xNR20_Example</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>This example configures Channel Filter driver for one NR100 carrier and three NR20 whit multiAddCC API and at the end close and release the driver. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The example does the following:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>initialize driver from reset to activation</para></listitem><listitem><para>configure filters with the pre-calculated coefficients</para></listitem><listitem><para>Get current configuration.</para></listitem><listitem><para>add 4 carriers CCID={0,1,2,3}, 1xNR100(122.88Msps) and 3xNR20(30.72Msps)</para></listitem><listitem><para>Trigger configuration update.</para></listitem><listitem><para>at this point filters are set and ready to operate</para></listitem><listitem><para>close the driver</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para><simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if the example has completed successfully.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE if the example has failed.//! [testexample3] </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
